lastCommitMessage: refactor: update tab initialization and loading logic in order management and splash pages

- Modified the tab initialization process in SellerOrderManagementPage and OrdersTabPage to set the tab length directly in initState and moved the initialization logic to didChangeDependencies for better lifecycle management.
- Enhanced loading steps in SplashPage by initializing them in didChangeDependencies, ensuring proper setup during widget lifecycle.
- Improved logging for tab state changes and data loading in OrdersTabPage to provide better insights during debugging.
These changes streamline the tab management and loading processes, enhancing the overall performance and maintainability of the application.
